  Nng7 e5 hak8-seng mng7 in kong2, iau2 kam2 bo5 pat8 tiau5 lou7 thang jip8? 
  Nng7 lang5 kong2, U7, na7-si7 I2-lok8, I2-li7-a i2-goa7, tui3 khui thiN toe7 kau3 taN, iau2-be7 un2 lang5 kiaN5, chiu7 kau3 lou7-be2 jit8, ho7-thau5 tan5 hit-tiap8, iah8 bo5 lang5 kiaN5. 
  Ki-tok-tou5 sim chiu7 hoan5-lo2, Hian5-bong7 iah8 si7 an2-ni. Siang-peng5 si3-ui5 teh khoaN3, long2 bo5 pat8-hang7 ke3-ti3 thang m7-sai2 tui3 chit-e5 ho5 ke3-khi3.Hit-tiap8 chiu7 mng7 Ng7 lang5 kong2, Ho5 chui2 tak8 sou2-chai7 long2 si7 chhim mah? 
  Nng7 lang5 kong2, Khiok bo5, chong2-si7 kau3 chia goan2 boe7 chan7 lin2. Tioh8 khoaN3 lin2 e5 sin3 si7 toa7, si7 soe3, chiah oe7 chai chit-e5 ho5 e5 chhim, khin2. 
  Nng7 e5 hak8-seng chiu7 tui3 ho5-nih khi3, Ki-tok-tou5 chit8-e7 jip8-khi3, un5-un5-a2 tim5 loh8-khi3, toa7 siaN-au5 Hian5-bong7 kong2, Goa2 tim5 hi2 chhim chui2--nih8, chui2 e5 toa7 eng2 long2 im goa2 e5 thau5-khak. 
  Hian5-bong7 kong2, An2-hiaN li2 m7-sai2 kiaN, goa2 u7 tah8-tioh8 i e5 toe2, chai--kio3 u7 sit8-toe7. 
  Ki-tok-tou5 kong2, ¡§Si2 kap hoan5-lo2 tiN5 goa2, lau5 leng lau5 bit8 e5 sou2-chai7, goa2 tek-khak boe7-tit-thang khoaN3-kiN3.¡¨ Hit-tiap8 ou-am3 kap kiaN-hiaN5 long2 kau3 Ki-tok-tou5, i peh chiuN7-lai5 hit-tiap8, khoaN3 long2 boe7 kiN3, chha-put-to put-seng2 jin5-su7; chit lou7 sou2 tit-tioh8 e5 un-tian2, an-ui3, long2 boe7 ki3-tit. i hit-tiap8 teh kong2, long2 si7 kong2 hoan5-lo2 kap kiaN-hiaN5, kiaN-liau2 si2 hi2 ho5--nih8, boe7-tit-thang jip8 thiN-siaN5. Hit-tiap8 siuN7--tioh8 kau3 cheng5 e5 choe7, i e5 sim chin7-chai7 hoan5-lo2. Hit-tiap8 ia7 u7 ka7 piN-a2 e5 lang5 kong2, kong2--kio3 u7 Mou5-kui2 lai5 tiN5--i, chiah kau3 chit tiap8. Hian5-bong7 chiu7 na7 chhut-lat8 beh hu5--i, iah8 boe7 bian2-tit i e5 thau5-khak boe7 tim3-loh8-khi3, si7 i hit-tiap8-n2 chha-put-to beh si2, pou7-pin5 u7 hoan--khi2-lai5. 
  Hian5-bong7 chiah an-ui3 i kong2, An2-hiaN--ah! goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 hit e5 mng5, teng2-bin7 u7 lang5 teh khia7, tit-beh chih-chiap lan2. 
  Ki-tok-tou5 kong2, i si7 chih-chiap li2, m7-si7 beh chih-chiap goa2, si7 li2 kap goa2 siong-sek8 kau3 taN, phin2-heng7 thang o-lo2. 
  Hian5-bong7 kong2, An2-hiaN--ah! li2 e5 phin2-heng7 sit8-chai7 thang o-lo2. 
  Ki-tok-tou5 kong2, An2-hiaN--ah! goa2 na7 chin-chiaN3 si7 an2-ni, Chu2 taN siaN2-su7 m7 kiu3 goa2? I si7 khoaN3 goa2 u7 choe7, chiah chhoa7 goa2 kau3 hi2 ham7-khiN--nih8 pang3 hiat-kak8 goa2. 
  Hian5-bong7 kong2, Seng3-chheh u7 kong2, ¡§I si2 e5 cheng5-iu5, khoan-iong5 bo5 pe2-pak8, i e5 khui3-lat8 iau2 iong2, m7-si7 chhin-chhiuN7 pat8 lang5 e5 hoan5-lo2 kiau2-chha2, che sit8-chai7 si7 chi2 phaiN2 lang5 kong2.¡¨ An2-hiaN li2 kam2 boe7 ki3-tit mah? TaN an2-hiaN li2 tui3 chui2--nih8 u7 hoan5-lo2, kan-khou2. Eng7 che choe3 pin5-ku3, chin-chiaN3 m7-si7 Siong7-te3 m7-tih8, si7 Siong7-te3 beh chhi3 li2, khoaN3 li2 cheng5 tit-tioh8 i e5 un-tian2, taN oe7 ki3-tit a2 boe7. 
  Goa2 hit-tiap8 bang7--nih8 khoaN3-kiN3 Ki-tok-tou5 thiaN-kiN3 che, chit8-si5 ka-ki7 teh siuN7. Hian5-bong7 koh ka7 i kong2, An2-hiaN li2 m7-sai2 kiaN, Ia5-sou beh kiu3 li2. Ki-tok-tou5 chiah toa7 siaN kio3 kong2, Haih--ah! Goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 Chu2 u7 tui3 goa2 kong2, ¡§Li2 thang ke3 chiah-e5 chui2, Goa2 tek-khak beh kap li2 saN-kap ke3 chiah-e5 ho5, tek-khak boe7 im li2.¡¨ Nng7 e5 hak8-seng e5 sim tui3 chit-tiap8 long2 an2-ni, kau3 ke3 ho5 chiuN7 hoaN7. 
  Hit-tiap8 Ng7 e5 hak8-seng peh-chiuN7 hit peng5 hoaN7, hit-nih8 u7 Ng7 lang5 chheng7 chin7-chai7 kng e5 saN teh theng3-hau7, beh chih-chiap in. Kau3 in hia, Ng7 lang5 u7 ka7 in kong2, Goan2 si7 chhe-eng7 e5 sit8, thoe3 tit-beh tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 lang5, hou7 i thang chhe-eng7, soa3 thang hok8-sai7 i; chiah saN-kap kiaN5, un5-un5-a2 tui3 siaN5-mng5 khi3. Chit e5 siaN5 si7 khi2 ti7 hit-e5 koaiN5 soaN-teng2. Nng7 e5 hak8-seng peh-chiuN7 hia, si7 u7 Ng7 lang5 khan--i, chiah peh chin khoai3. Hit-tiap8 kap Ng7 e5 lang5 teh kong2 oe7 chMn7 hoaN-hi2, si7 in-ui7 ke3 ho5 long2 bo5 hai7, koh si7 in-ui7 u7 chit8-Ng7 lang5 thang saN-sang3. In hit-tiap8 teh kong2, long2 si7 kong2 thiN-siaN5 e5 eng5-kng. Hi2 Ng7 lang5 u7 kong2 thiN-siaN5 e5 eng5-kng, si7 kong2 long2 boe7 liau2. In koh kong2, ¡§Hit--nih8 u7 Sun5-soaN, thiN-teng2 e5 Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2, thiN-sai3 choe3 chit8 tui, u7 chheng-chheng ban7-ban7; koh u7 gi7--e5 sin3 tit-tioh8 thiN2--nih8 chiau5-chng5 e5 hok-khi3.¡¨ Koh kong2, Lin2 taN beh khi3 Siong7-te3 e5 lok8-hng5, oe7-tit-thang khoaN3-kiN3 oah8-mia7 e5 chhiu7, soa3 thang chiah8 i e5 ho2 ke2-chi2, lin2 kau3 hit--nih8, tek-khak eng7 peh8 saN siuN2-su3 lin2, tak8-jit8 thang kap Chu2 saN-kap kong2, saN-kap kiaN5, tak8 tai7 bo5 soah.Koh kong2, Lin2 tiam3 se3-kan u7 hoan5-lo2, piN7-thiaN3, kan-khou2, oe7 si2, chiah-e5 tai7-chi3, tui3 chia kau3 be2 boe7 koh khoaN3-kiN3 che.Koh kong2, Cheng5 e5 tai7-chi3 ke3 liau2, lin2 taN tit-beh kun7 A-pek-liap8-han2, I2-sat, Nga2-kok, chiah e5 sian-ti lang5. 
  Nng7 e5 hak8-seng mng7 i kong2, Goan2 kau3 thiN-siaN5, tioh8 choe3 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3? in kong2, Lin2 kau3 hit--nih8 tek-khak chiong thoa-boa5 oaN7 khoaN3-oat8, chiong hoan5-lo2 oaN7 hoaN-hi2. Lin2 cheng5 tiam3 se3-kan khui siaN ki5-to2, lau5 bak8-sai2, ui7-tioh8 Chu2 siu7 kan-khou2, kau3 hit--nih8 tek-khak tit-tioh8 i e5 ke2-chi2; koh tek-khak thang ti3 kim e5 bian2-liu5, thiN-nih seng3 e5 Chu2 tak8 si5 oe7-tit-thang khoaN3-kiN3. Lin2 cheng5 tiam3 se3-kan, sit8-chai7 si7 ai3 hok8-sai7 Chu2, na7-si7 seng-khu teh hok8-sai7 si7 cham2-jian5 oh, taN lin2 kau3 hit--nih8, tek-khak eng2-eng2 hok8-sai7 Chu2, o-lo2, hoaN-hi2, kong2 to-sia7 tak8 si5 bo5 ia3. Ti7 hia tak8 hang7 oe7 e5 Chu2, lin2 e5 bak8-chiu tek-khak hoaN-hi2 khoaN3-kiN3 i e5 eng5-kng, hi7-khang iah8 hoaN-hi2 thiaN i e5 siaN.Koh lin2 khia7 hit--nih8 tek-khak tit-tioh8 eng5-kng e5 saN thang chheng7, eng5-kng e5 chhia thang che7, thang kap eng5-kng e5 Chu2 saN-kap kiaN5. Kau3 Chu2 che7 thiN-hun5 koh lai5, ho7-thau5 toa7 siaN tan5, lin2 iah8 oe7-tit-thang kap I saN-kap khi3. Chu2 che7 sim2-mng7 e5 che7-ui7, lin2 iah8 oe7-tit-thang tiam3 i piN-a2 teh khia7. Koh kiam2-chhai2 si7 phaiN2 sin5, si7 phaiN2 lang5, hit-tiap8 Chu2 toan7 i u7 choe7, lin2 iah8 oe7-tit-thang kap i saN-kap toan3. Koh Chu2 to3-khi3 thiN-siaN5--nih8, lin2 iah8 thang kap i saN-kap to3-khi3, eng2-eng2 kap i khia7. 
  Hit-tiap8 tai7-ke an2-ni saN-kap kong2, chiam7-chiam7 kun7 siaN5-mng5, pou7-pin5 u7 choe7-choe7 thian-kun chhut-lai5 chih-chiap in. Nng7 e5 kng-kng e5 lang5 ka7 thiN-peng kong2, Chi2 Ng7 lang5 chiu7-si7 tiam3 se3-kan u7 thiaN3 Chu2, ui7-tioh8 Chu2 pang3 hiat-kak8 i sou2 u7. Chu2 chhe goan2 toa3 in lai5, taN i2-keng kau3 chia lah, thang hou7 in jip8 siaN5, oe7-tit-thang kiN3-tioh8 Chu2 e5 bin7.Hit-tiap8 thian-kun u7 hoaN-hi2 kiong-hi2 kong2, ¡§KiN3-u7 tit-beh che7 iuN5-ko chhoa7-bou2 e5 toh-e5, u7 hok-khi3.¡¨ Hit-tiap8 koh u7 Chu2 e5 gak8-kong chhut-lai5 chih-chiap--in. In e5 saN peh8 koah kng, siaN toa7 koah ho5, un7 kau3 hi2 thiN--nih8. Nng7 e5 hak8-seng li7 se3-kan kau3 chia u7 choe7-choe7 gak8-kong toa7-toa7 ka7 in kiong-hi2. In ui5 Ng7 e5 hak8-seng, u7 e5 thau5-cheng5, u7 e5 au7-piah, u7 e5 to3-peng5, u7 e5 chiaN3-peng5, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 beh chiau3-kou3 in, hou7 in thang peh-chiuN7 teng2-bin7. chit8 lou7 chok-gak8 siaN long2 ho5-ho5, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 thiN lai5 kau3 in tau. cheng3-lang5 an2-ni chin3-cheng5 kiaN5, gak8-kong hoaN-hi2, tak8-si5 chiap8-chiap8 chok-gak8, thiau3-bu2, i3-su3 si7 beh Ng7 e5 hak8-seng chai, in si7 hoaN-hi2 lai5 chih-chiap in. Hit-tiap8 Ng7 e5 hak8-seng khiok be7 jip8 siaN5, i2-keng u7 chhin-chhiuN7 tiam3 thiN nih8 e5 hoaN-hi2, i e5 sim chin7 khoaN3-oah8 kau3 boe7-kou3-tit. Hit-tiap8 kiaN5 kau3 chia, siaN5 long2 u7 khoaN3-kiN3, hong2-hut u7 thiaN-kiN3, siaN5 nih8 u7 cheng-kou2 e5 siaN, chhin-chhiuN7 beh lai5 chih-chiap in jip8 khi3. Nng7 e5 hak8-seng chiu7 kiaN5 kau3 siaN5-mng5. Hit-tiap8 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 mng5-teng2 u7 kim ji7 kong2, ¡§KiN3 u7 than3 Chu2 e5 tiau5-kai3--e5, u7 hok-khi3, thang tit-tioh8 oah8-mia7 e5 chhiu7, tui3 mng5 jip8 siaN5.¡¨
  Hit-tiap8 goa2 bang7-kiN3 Ng7 e5 eng5-kng--e5 hoan-hu3 Ng7 e5 hak8-seng tioh8 phah mng5. Phah liau2 u7 lang5 tui3 mng5-teng2 khoaN3 loh8-lai5, chiu7-si7 I2-lok8, Mou5-se, I2-li7-a chiah e5.cheng3-lang5 ka7 in kong2, chit Ng7 e5 hak8-seng ui7-tioh8 thiaN3 Chu2 u7 li7 Chiong-bong5 siaN5 lai5. Nng7 e5 hak8-seng cheng5 sou2 tit-tioh8 e5 chip-chio3, hit-tiap8 theh8-chhut-lai5 kau, liam5-piN u7 lang5 chiong chip-chio3 theh8 hou7 Chu2. Chu2 khoaN3 soah, chiu7 kong2, Hiah e5 lang5 toh8-loh8? In3 i kong2, Chit-tiap8 ti7 hi2 mng5-goa7. 
  Chu2 chiu7 kah--i mng5 tioh8 liam5-piN khui, hou7 in jip8-lai5. 
  Goa2 bang7-kiN3 Ng7 e5 hak8-seng hit-tiap8 jip8 thiN-siaN5, chit8-e7 jip8, bin7 chiu7 pian3 sek, u7 chheng7 saN kng-kng chhin-chhiuN7 kim. Koh u7 lang5 chin3-cheng5 theh8 khim5 kap bian2-liu5 siuN2-su3 in. Hit-e5 khim5 si7 o-lo2 Chu2 thang eng7, hit-e5 bian2-liu5 chiu7-si7 chun-kui3 e5 bo7. Hit-tiap8 goa2 bang7-kiN3 thong siaN5 e5 cheng-kou2 toa7 siaN teh tan5, Chu2 ka7 in kong2, ¡§Lin2 tioh8 jip8-lai5, siu7-tioh8 Goa2 e5 hoaN-hi2.¡¨ 
  Goa2 iah8 u7 thiaN-kiN3 Ng7 e5 hak8-seng toa7 siaN teh chhiuN3 kong2, ¡§Ai3 hok-khi3, chun-kui3, eng5-kng, koan5-leng5, khui3-lat8 kui hou7 che7 thiN-ui7--e5, soa3 kui hou7 IuN5-ko, tak8-tai7 bo5 soa3¡¨. 
  Mng5 tu2-a2 khui, Ng7 e5 hak8-seng jip8-khi3, goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 hi2 lai7-bin7, siaN5 e5 kng chhin-chhiuN7 jit8, koe-lou7 long2 si7 phou ng5-kim. SiaN5-lai7 u7 choe7-choe7 lang5 teh kiaN5, thau5 ti3 kim e5 bian2-liu5, chhiu2 kiah8 cho2-ki, kap kim khim5. Koh goa2 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 cheng3-lang5 e5 chiong5-tiong, seng-khu u7 sit8--e5, eng2-eng2 saN-kap toa7 siaN kio3 kong2, ¡§Seng3--ah! Seng3--ah! Seng3--ah! Goa2 e5 Chu2 Siong7-te3.¡¨ Au7-lai5 mng5 chiah koaiN. Goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 che, iah8 chin7-chai7 ai3 tiam3 hit--nih8. 
  Goa2 hit-tiap8 tu2-a2 teh khoaN3, pou7-pin5 oat8 ke3-khi3, khoaN3-kiN3 Bu5-ti kun7 ho5-piN, ke3 ho5 chin kin2, long2 bo5 chhin-chhiuN7 Ng7 e5 hak8-seng e5 kan-khou2. Si7 i hit-tiap8 kau3 chia, pou7-pin5 u7 tu2-tioh8 chit8-e5 tou7-thau5--e5, mia5 kio3 Hu-bong7, eng7 sio2 chun5 chai3 i ke3-khi3. Bu5-ti iah8 piN5-piN5 peh-chiuN7 soaN, beh kau3 siaN5-mng5, na7-si7 i hit-tiap8 ku2 si7 cheng7-cheng7 ka-ki7 teh kiaN5, long2 bo5 chit lang5 chhut-lai5 chih-chiap--i. I2-keng kau3 thiN-mng5, kiah8 thau5 khoaN3-kiN3 mng5 teng2 e5 kim-ji7, iah8 phah mng5, liong7 mng5 tek-khak liam5-piN khui, thang kap i jip8-khi3. Mng5 teng2 aN3 teh khoaN3 e5 lang5 u7 mng7 i kong2, Li2 tui3 toh8-loh8 lai5? ai3 tit-tioh8 sim2-mih8? 
  Bu5-ti kong2, Goa2 cheng5 bat tiam3 Chu2 e5 bin7-cheng5 lim-chiah8, Chu2 u7 bat tiam3 goan2 hit--nih8 ka3-si7. Hit-tiap8 mng5 teng2 e5 lang5 u7 beh tui3 i theh8 chip-chio3, khi3 kau hou7 Chu2, Bu5-ti tui3 tou2-koaN7 si3-koe3 chhiau, long2 bo5. Hit-tiap8 chiu7 mng7 Bu5-ti kong2, Li2 kam2 bo5 mah? 
  Bu5-ti e2-e2 long2 bo5 poaN3-ku3 oe7 thang kong2.Mng5-teng2 e5 lang5 eng7 che oe7 po3 hou7 Chu2 chai.Chu2 m7 loh8-lai5 kiN3--i, chiah kah Ng7 e5 eng5-kng e5 lang5 chhut-khi3 pak8 i e5 kha chhiu2, liah8 i khi3. 
  Nng7 e5 lang5 liam5-piN chhut-khi3 liah8 Bu5-ti, tui3 poan3-khong-tiong khi3, kau3 cheng5 sou2 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 soaN-mng5, chiah hiat i lai7-bin7. Goa2 hit-tiap8 teh siuN7, chai--kio3 m7-na7 tui3 Chiong-bong5 siaN5 u7 lou7 thang thang3 te7-gek8, chiu7 tui3 thiN-mng5 iah8 u7 lou7 thang thang3 te7-gek8. 
  Goa2 bang7-kau3 chia chiah chhiN2, chiah u7 gim5 chit8-siu2 si kong2, 
  Bang7-lai7 u7 oe7 in2 Seng3-keng, <BR>ChiuN-chiuN ku3-ku3 koe2 hun-beng5; <BR>Put-lun7 peng5-iu2 kap hiaN-ti7, <BR>Tioh8 eng7 che oe7 saN chi2-si7. <BR>Kau3-kham3 lai5 kiaN5 chin to7-li2, <BR>Boh8-tit loe2-chi3 koa3 poeh-si2; <BR>Chin3-cheng5 phi3-ju7 hou7 lin2 chai, <BR>Ai3 lin2 ki3-liam7 khng3 sim-lai7. <BR>Chit tiau5 chiu7-si7 thian-tong5 lou7, <BR>M7 tui3 chia khi3 chin7 chho3-gou7; <BR>Chit pun2 sou2 thoan5 kek8-ki5 ho2, <BR>Pi2 gun5 pi2 kim ban7 pe7 ho2. <BR>Kin2 chiong tak8 phiN lai5 hoan-ek8, <BR>Khou2-khng3 tai7-ke tioh8 beng5-pek8; <BR>Na7 liah8 sou2 bang7 choe3 bo5-ek, <BR>Kau3 be2 seng-khu loh8 te7-gek8. 
